These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, blood-red
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, dunhill
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, aconite
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, december
City: new-york, prague
House: tower, ranch-style
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| Color         | white   | blood-red     |
| Cigar           | chaman | dunhill   |
| Flower   | aconite   | tulip  |
| Birthday   | december | april |
| City           | new-york      | prague     |
| House     | ranch-style    | tower   |

