.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, prince
There 2 different types of food: plum, eggplant
2 different games are played: canasta, billiard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, tennis
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, fantasy
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, dahlia
1. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | iced-tea |
| Cigar         | prince        | aristoff  |
| Food           | plum | eggplant  |
| Game   | billiard            | canasta    |
| Sport   | handball     | tennis   |
| Movie-Genre           | zombie         | fantasy    |
| Flower     | sunflower           | dahlia      |

