.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, red
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, october
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, journalist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, classical
City: hannover, liverpool
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, gardening
2 different games are played: whist, poker
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who likes red is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person playing whist##1
4. the dancer is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Color      | fuchsia          | red       |
| Birthday          | october   | august   |
| Job           | journalist   | dancer     |
| Music-Genre   | soul | classical        |
| City           | hannover      | liverpool       |
| Hobby         | video-games       | gardening |
| Game     | whist          | poker |

