.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, zinnia
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, ivory
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, july
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, dubstep
2 different games are played: backgammon, bridge
City: colone, new-york
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, tram
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the fan of rock is the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Flower         | daffodil  | zinnia    |
| Color           | ivory       | lilac    |
| Birthday   | february | july    |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | dubstep |
| Game           | bridge      | backgammon      |
| City         | new-york     | colone    |
| Transport     | tram        | train     |

